---
title: Southwestern-Style Tofu and Ranch Salad with Charred Veggies
description: Spicy green peppers and corn pair perfectly with charred tofu  in this tantalizing meal that comes together with our fabulous Southwestern Spice Blend. It's easy, fast and packed with flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southwestern-style-tofu-and-ranch-salad-5ad775b2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/southwestern-style-tofu-and-ranch-salad-6536ad836919bfabf2058de7-9fddd808.pdf
